 avg_row_delete_log_duration    | 10 us       | 10 us         | INTERVAL   |          5
 avg_fkey_check_duration        | 20 us       | 20 us         | INTERVAL   |          6
 fixed_step_rollback_duration   | 2.5 ms      | 2.5 ms        | INTERVAL   |          7
